# Infra and Migration Caution

- Prefer incremental, single-service rollout over multi-service jumps.
- Keep cost controls visible (budget alerting and spend guardrails).
- Document assumptions and rollback steps for each infra change.
- Do not hardcode credentials; use secret manager and placeholders only.
- Update migration logs when milestones or runbooks change.

## Quick pass/fail check

- [ ] Change is incremental with rollback path
- [ ] No credentials or secret values introduced
- [ ] Cost and migration documentation updated as needed
